io.sphere.sdk.queries

Interface MetaModelQueryDsl<T,C extends MetaModelQueryDsl<T,C,Q,E>,Q,E>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - type of the query result
    C - type of the class implementing this class
    Q - type of the query model
    E - type of the expansion model
    All Superinterfaces:
    ExpansionPathContainer<T>, MetaModelReferenceExpansionDsl<T,C,E>, Query<T>, QueryDsl<T,C>, ReferenceExpansionDsl<T,C>, ReferenceExpansionSupport<T>, ResourceQuery<T>, SphereRequest<PagedQueryResult<T>>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    CartDiscountQuery, CartQuery, CategoryQuery, ChannelQuery, CustomerGroupQuery, CustomerQuery, CustomObjectQuery<T>, DiscountCodeQuery, InventoryEntryQuery, JsonNodeQuery, MessageQuery, OrderQuery, PaymentQuery, ProductDiscountQuery, ProductProjectionQuery, ProductQuery, ProductTypeQuery, ReviewQuery, ShippingMethodQuery, StateQuery, TaxCategoryQuery, TypeQuery, ZoneQuery
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    MetaModelQueryDslImpl

    public interface MetaModelQueryDsl<T,C extends MetaModelQueryDsl<T,C,Q,E>,Q,E>
extends ResourceQuery<T>, QueryDsl<T,C>, MetaModelReferenceExpansionDsl<T,C,E>
    Internal query request interface for immutable value classes which can copy themselves with modified fields providing a meta model for convenient creation of expressions.
